title: Why Apple Stock Tasted Sour on Tuesday
description: Apple (NASDAQ: AAPL) shareholders had a trading session to forget on Tuesday.  Before the session opened, AllianceBernstein prognosticator Toni Sacconaghi published a new Apple research note.  On top of that, its gross margins fell in its most recently reported quarter.

title: Markets Tumble on Inflation and Interest Rate Worries
description: U.S. stocks posted sharp declines on Tuesday, Feb. 21, with interest rate concerns and reports from retailers weighing on the markets.
